&lt;p&gt;The first topic "Building mobile applications", Gaosboy with his development practices and lessons learned, focus on the optimization of the performance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The second topic is by Luo Guanghui, about "Chrome Courgette", combined with his own previous products the actual update needs,  do a very detailed explanation and live demonstration of the DEMO.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Break links, Hangzhou GTUG the organizers, play the china GTUGs video, to facilitate other cities's GTUG situation, and feel the vitality of the GTUGs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Later third theme is Zooboa, "Web Application Security Analysis", a deep accumulation of Zooboa in the technical aspects of information security attack and defense, the speech content is very rich, and give a lot of practical advice.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The final topic, is the Mark Huang, he brought the "Python Virtualenv &amp; Virtualenv Wrapper ", he like python very much, but he hate java:-)&lt;/p&gt;
